Ubiquity for Opera - List of changes

2010-09-14
    - Added "duckduckgo" command to search on duckduckgo.com
    - Fixed a bug in the Google default search command

2010-06-24
    - Added the "bing" command to search with www.bing.com

2010-04-29
    - Fixed ubiq_focus() function to work in Opera 10.5+
    - Added the ESC key binding, to hide the Ubiquity window

2010-01-24
    - Added the "shorten-url" command. Uses bit.ly API
    - Added the minified version, ubiquity-min.js

The rest of the history is not tracked.

See http://my.opera.com/cstrep/blog/show.dml/tag/ubiquity

